I come to rants to ... well, rant.  Sometimes this may be a political rant, sometimes it is me calling certain posters idiots and showing them why.  Having them all split up just means that I check one and ignore the rest.<br>
<br>
(2) Please don’t lock polls.  <br>
From time to time discussions break out in them that get very entertaining.  I would agree to locking them after they are dead for a number of days, but s long as they are going leave them alone.  I find them entertaining.<br>
<br>
(3) Id has a good point.<br>
Simplicity is best, and since we do this (some of us, anyway) for entertainment, we are not as likely to click around the entire board as we are to check the sections we have interest in.  Yes, there are deviations, but for the most part, the fewer categories we have to check, the better.<br>
<br>
